OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBank of England considers  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fraising saver protection   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Bank of England is considering     
OL,6, raising the level of protection given  
OL,7, to bank savings, following recent      
OL,8, upheaval in the financial sector.      
OL,10,FCurrently, deposits up to #85,000 are  
OL,11,Fprotected if a bank fails, far less    
OL,12,Fthan in US banks.                      
OL,14,FBank of England governor Andrew Bailey 
OL,15,Fsaid he did not believe there was a    
OL,16,Frisk of a 2008-style crisis.           
OL,18,FBut he questioned whether UK banks were
OL,19,Fholding enough liquidity - or available
OL,20,Fcash - to cope with short-term shocks. 
